video.title: Power Rangers Wild Force
video.synopsis: Raised in the wilderness, young Cole Evans leads the Wild Force Power Rangers as they summon their animal powers to battle the evil Master Org.

episodes.synopsis: A young man raised in the jungle travels to the city of Turtle Cove and discovers an island floating in the sky above the metropolis.
episodes.title: Lionheart

episodes.synopsis: While Cole attempts to reason with the Barbed Wire Org, Jindrax and Toxica discover that after 3,000 years, Master Org has returned to Earth.
episodes.title: Darkness Awakening

episodes.synopsis: Taylor struggles to accept Cole's leadership.
episodes.title: Click, Click, Zoom

episodes.synopsis: The return of Danny's former crush strains his close friendship with Max.
episodes.title: Never Give Up!

episodes.synopsis: During a university field trip to some caves, Alyssa discovers an ancient relic from the Kingdom of Animaria.
episodes.title: Ancient Awakening

episodes.synopsis: Max writes a wish on a note, puts it inside a bottle and throws it into Turtle Lake.
episodes.title: Wishes on the Water

episodes.synopsis: Taylor helps two mysterious twin boys while reflecting on how she became the first Wild Force Ranger.
episodes.title: The Bear Necessities

episodes.synopsis: While searching for the Soul Bird to heal the injured Red Lion Zord, Cole comes face-to-face with Master Org.
episodes.title: Soul Searching

episodes.synopsis: Master Org's former bodyguard, Retinax, fights the Power Rangers to restore his lost honor.
episodes.title: Soul Bird Salvation

episodes.synopsis: Gen. Org Nayzor unseals an ancient tomb, freeing a cursed warrior with the face of a wolf.
episodes.title: Curse of the Wolf

episodes.synopsis: Zen-Aku battles the Rangers with his evil Wild Zords.
episodes.title: Battle of the Zords

episodes.synopsis: Jindrax and Toxica hijack a bus full of innocents to coerce Max into giving up his Animal Crystal.
episodes.title: Predazord, Awaken

episodes.synopsis: Taylor and the Rangers rally to rescue Princess Shayla from Zen-Aku.
episodes.title: Revenge of Zen-Aku

episodes.synopsis: Fearing that Zen-Aku's memory is returning, Nayzor coerces him into attacking the Power Rangers with their own Zords.
episodes.title: Identity Crisis

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers learn Zen-Aku's true identity and how he became an evil warrior for the Orgs.
episodes.title: The Ancient Warrior

episodes.synopsis: The ancient Animarian warrior Merrick fights to atone for his past misdeeds.
episodes.title: The Lone Wolf

episodes.synopsis: A mysterious new Org general fights the Rangers. Meanwhile, Merrick finds a new home.
episodes.title: Power Play

episodes.synopsis: While Alyssa helps Cole search for information about his long-lost parents, Master Org tries to hide his past from Jindrax and Toxica.
episodes.title: Secrets and Lies

episodes.synopsis: To help defeat a peculiar new Org, Max tries to enlist the aid of his former bowling mentor.
episodes.title: The Tornado Spin

episodes.synopsis: Danny competes with a wealthy rival for Kendall's affections while trying to prevent the Wedding Dress Org from capturing Turtle Cove's brides-to-be.
episodes.title: Three's a Crowd

episodes.synopsis: Alyssa must rely on her martial arts heritage when the Rangers come up against Samurai Org.
episodes.title: A Father's Footsteps

episodes.synopsis: The Tombstone Org attempts to put the Rangers 6 feet under while Merrick and the Princess try to appease the only Zord capable of saving them.
episodes.title: Sing Song

episodes.synopsis: Nayzor returns more powerful than ever, requiring the Rangers to travel across time and space to find help from a new Zord.
episodes.title: The Wings of Animaria

episodes.synopsis: The Wild Force Rangers team with the Silver Guardians to stop three time-traveling monsters from the year 3001.
episodes.title: Reinforcements from the Future: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The Power Rangers Time Force travels back in time to help the Power Rangers Wild Force prevent the three Mut-Orgs from teaming with Master Org.
episodes.title: Reinforcements from the Future: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Cole learns the truth about his parents when Master Org reveals his sinister origin to the Wild Force Rangers.
episodes.title: The Master's Last Stand

episodes.synopsis: When Zen-Aku returns to claim Merrick's soul, he must confront a demon from his past.
episodes.title: Unfinished Business

episodes.synopsis: Cole must protect a young amnesiac as Mandilok, the new Org general, unleashes two Duke Orgs on the city.
episodes.title: Homecoming

episodes.synopsis: Princess Shayla and Merrick argue as the Flute Org's music ruins their song, causing the Rangers to dance uncontrollably.
episodes.title: The Flute

episodes.synopsis: While Max and Taylor help Kite look for his home, they're attacked at an amusement park by Jindrax and his brother, Juggalo.
episodes.title: Team Carnival

episodes.synopsis: The Lion Tamer Org takes control of the Wild Zords and turns them against the Rangers.
episodes.title: Taming of the Zords

episodes.synopsis: Kite finally remembers his past while growing angry about humankind's indifference toward nature.
episodes.title: Monitoring Earth

episodes.synopsis: Even without Princess Shayla and the Wild Zords, the Rangers refuse to give up their fight to save the world.
episodes.title: The Soul of Humanity

episodes.synopsis: Red Rangers from 10 different teams unite to stop the Machine Empire from using Serpentera to destroy Earth.
episodes.title: Forever Red

episodes.synopsis: Duke Org Onikage arrives in the Nexus with a plan to infiltrate the Rangers' Animarium and capture Princess Shayla.
episodes.title: The Master's Herald: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The Power Rangers fight across dimensions to try to rescue Princess Shayla from the returning Master Org.
episodes.title: The Master's Herald: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: As Jindrax plots to bring back his friend Toxica, the Rangers receive help from an unlikely source in their battle against the powerful Locomotive Org.
episodes.title: Fishing for a Friend

episodes.synopsis: Jindrax and Toxica team with the Rangers to rescue the Princess and destroy the Nexus once and for all.
episodes.title: Sealing the Nexus

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers realize that their time as superheroes is at an end. Meanwhile, in the remains of the Nexus, a new threat emerges.
episodes.title: The End of the Power Rangers: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Master Org's destruction of nature continues unchecked while the Power Rangers fight a last desperate battle for the planet.
episodes.title: The End of the Power Rangers: Part 2
